<br>
<b>Meetings</b>: 
<br>
<br>
Classes: Mondays, Wednesdays, and Fridays, 10:10AM--11:00AM in LGRT 1234.
<br>

<br>
Office hours: Mondays 4:00PM--5:00PM and Tuesdays 3:00--4:00PM, in my office LGRT 1235H.
